skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: texas lakes
des: Texas Lakes provides lake level information for 121 lakes in Texas. In addition, it can provide the weekly fishing report from the Texas Parks & Wildlife website. All data is publicly available from waterdatafortexas.org or tpwd.texas.gov.
